comment: Monroe (MIL) sets the screen on Gibson (CHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gasol (CHI) firms up as he sets the screen on Carter-Williams (MIL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
LHH shows that Middleton (MIL) and Carter-Williams (MIL) maintain legal guarding position as Butler (CHI) attempts to split the double team and loses control of the ball.
Gibson (CHI) dislodges Antetokounmpo (MIL), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Butler (CHI) sets the screen on Carter-Williams (MIL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Carter-Williams (MIL) makes contact with Butler's (CHI) arm that affects his jump shot attempt. The contact occurs during Butler's upward shooting motion and this is a shooting foul.
After communicating with the Replay Center, there was conclusive video evidence that showed that Butler (CHI) was behind the line when he was fouled by Carter-Williams (MIL).
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes incidental contact with Butler (CHI) that does not affect his RSBQ at the start of the drive.
LHH shows that Monroe (MIL) establishes a legal guarding position and jumps vertically to contest Butler's (CHI) driving layup attempt.
Gasol (CHI) grabs Antetokounmpo (MIL) after he secures the rebound.
Gasol (CHI) grabs Monroe (MIL) after he secures the rebound.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of a 3 point field goal by Gasol (CHI) was confirmed.
